[[Image:Owatatsumi-jinja2.JPG|thumb|right|Watatsumi Shrine in [[Sumiyoshi-ku, Osaka]]]]
There are numerous [[Shinto shrine]]s dedicated to the sea god Watatsumi. Some examples include the Ōwatatsumi jinja or Daikai jinja 大海神社 in [[Sumiyoshi-ku, Osaka]] (associated with the [[Sumiyoshi Taisha]] shrine), the {{ill|Watatsumi Shrine_(Kobe)|lt=Watatsumi Shrine|ja|海神社 (神戸市)|simple|Watatsumi Shrine}} 海神社 in [[Tarumi-ku, Kobe]], and the Watatsumi jinja 綿都美神社 in [[Kokura Minami-ku, Kitakyūshū]].

